Thank You for downloading this free and compact web based software. It is a free to use software coded in PHP and HTML.

-------------------------
   F E A T U R E S:
-------------------------
* Simple to Configure
* Compact in Size
* No Database required
* 50 pre-added quotes
* Secure Quotes File
* Simple Installation
* Fast Initialization

-------------------------
   C R E D I T S:
-------------------------
* Code Drops
* Shashwat Mishra

-------------------------
R E Q U I R E M E N T S:
-------------------------
* PHP 5.0+
* Apache 2.4+
* MySQL 4.2+

-------------------------
I N S T A L L A T I O N:
-------------------------
* Extract the Pacquotes1.3-nodb.zip archive to your root folder or wherever you want.
* Open 'config.php' file and edit your website's details.
* Run the 'subs.php' file by going to 'http://www.your-pacquotes-site.com/subs.php'.
* After a Success Message delete the 'subs.php' file.
* Now add more quotes to your site by editing the quotes 'txt' file. Add a new quote on a new line i.e. One Quote per Line.
* Hurraaahhh!!! Your are done! Enjoy your newly installed software.
* Now open the 'start.php' file and subscribe to our list to get the latest through e-mail.
